data.description:
Newly renovated 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath, single car garage, Town home. Located close to HEB, Randolph Air Force base, Forum Shopping, easy access to the 35, 1604, and Interstate 10. Great school district.

Tenant pays trash and electricity. Flat fee for water.
